.TH VV-CONTEXT 1 "2026-03-03" "vv v0.5.0-3-g664952a" "Vibe-Vault Manual"
.SH NAME
vv-context \- manage vault\-resident AI context files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B vv context [init | migrate]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Manages AI workflow context files (resume, iterations, tasks) that live
in the Obsidian vault rather than as untracked repo\-local files. This
makes context portable, searchable, and visible to Obsidian.
.PP
Subcommands:
  vv context init      Scaffold vault\-resident context for current project
  vv context migrate   Copy existing local files to vault
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR vv (1),
.BR vv\-context\-init (1),
.BR vv\-context\-migrate (1)
